(363230, 11399, 363222, 'Enigmatic Desires', 430, '', 1367930278, 'Well it depends on what U need to use it for. i would not recommend it for concealed carry since it is not a concealable weapon, rather an issue weapon for the army. On the + side it is extremely reliable! \n\nFor CC and reliability there is the NP 34. but again the same issue no manual safety albait a decocker. \n\nOn the other hand if U want a carry weapon then the NP 42 (2nd generation Cf 98) is a good gun. loaded chamber indicator. assasory rail manual safety decocker rotating barrel for low muzzle flip. Light waight and around 44k in karachi. And not very bulky.', 1, 1, '61.5.135.163', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
